Name: olfactory neuroblastoma
Definition: A mitochondrial encephalomyopathy that is characterized by mitochondrial myopathy

Name: olfactory neural tumor
Definition: A rhinitis which is persistent and long-lasting. It may occur with diseases such as syphilis

Name: obsolete transitional cell carcinoma of the ureter with squamous differentiation
Definition: A rhinitis which is persistent and long-lasting. It may occur with diseases such as syphilis
Synonym: ureteral transitional cell carcinoma with squamous differentiation
